### Contacts API Testing

# Development URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
# Production URL
# @baseUrl = https://cse-341-project1-okdp.onrender.com

### Get all contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts

### Get single contact by ID (replace with actual ID from get all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/65d7a8c1f1c2d3e4f5g6h7i8

### Create a new contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1990-05-15"
}

